    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、かっこ良くなるために\n今日から特訓する……！",
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、特訓って何をすればいい？",
      "startTime": 6.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺に聞かれても困るが……そうだな……\nかっこいい言葉を言ってみるのはどうだ？",
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういうセリフを言う時は\n自然と顔つきもかっこ良くなるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、やってみる……！",
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "――初めての挫折を、私達が味わわせてあげる\n……キリッ！",
      "startTime": 29.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……どう、かな？",
      "startTime": 31.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんというか……微妙だな……\nもしかして、今のは莉央さんの真似か？",
      "startTime": 37.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "そう。莉央さんをイメージしてみた……\nかっこいいと言えば、リズノワだから……",
      "startTime": 44.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、アイドル好きな雫らしいな\nでもここは別の言葉にした方がいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 51.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。違う言葉にする……\nそれじゃあ……",
      "startTime": 58.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "――僕はカニカマとずるいことは嫌いなんだ\n……キリッ！",
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "……どう、かな？",
      "startTime": 65.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "葵の真似になっただけじゃないか\nそれに、いちいちキメ顔しないといけないのか？",
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "これもダメ……？　難しい……",
      "startTime": 73.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、かっこいいって何……？\n見た目……？　仕草……？　雰囲気……？",
      "startTime": 81,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "それが分からないと、特訓にならない……\nもっと勉強しないと……",
      "startTime": 88.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、勉強するって……一体どうしたら……\n……はっ！",
      "startTime": 96.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7566.666666699987,
          "startTime": 104.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "そういう人を観察して極意を学ぶ……\nうん、それがいい……ちょっと観察して来る……！",
      "startTime": 101.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、雫！？\n……観察するって、何をするつもりだ？",
      "startTime": 108.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "雫のやつ、どこに行ったんだ？\n……ん？　あれはスリクスか？",
      "startTime": 117.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3099.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 120.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "これから出かけるみたいだな\nそして、三人の後ろをこそこそ歩いているのは……",
      "startTime": 123.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　{user}さん……！",
      "startTime": 128.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "雫？　そこで何をしているんだ？",
      "startTime": 130.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "今は話し掛けないで……\n尾行してるのがバレる",
      "startTime": 135.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "私はどうしても、かっこ良さの秘訣を知りたい\nだからスリクスを観察してる……",
      "startTime": 142.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それなら直接話を聞けばいいじゃないか",
      "startTime": 145.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "無理。スリクスは憧れの存在……\n目が合っただけで緊張する……",
      "startTime": 151.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "だから隠れて観察してる……\n先輩の仕事を見て、技術を盗む……それがプロ……！",
      "startTime": 157.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "職人っぽいことを言っているが\n話し掛ける度胸がないだけだよな？",
      "startTime": 164.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "私は尾行中だから、もう行く……\nそれじゃ……",
      "startTime": 170,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3366.6666667000127,
          "startTime": 170.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待った\n実はさっき、franさんからメッセージがきたんだ",
      "startTime": 172.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "「変な子にストーカー行為されてるから\nマネージャーならなんとかして」って……",
      "startTime": 178.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
